<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="MH Movers and Truck — Professional moving and construction services in Halifax, Nova Scotia. Residential & commercial moves, decks, fencing, roofing. Fully insured. Call (902) 943-3003.">
  <title>MH Movers and Truck — Moving & Construction Services | Halifax, NS</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="assets/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="header" id="header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="#" class="logo">
        <img src="assets/photos/photo_008.jpg" alt="MH Movers Logo" class="logo-img">
        <span class="logo-text"><strong>&amp; Truck</strong></span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav" id="nav">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#gallery">Our Work</a>
        <a href="#testimonials">Reviews</a>
        <a href="#areas">Areas</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Get a Free Quote</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-tag">Fully Insured &amp; Experienced Movers</p>
        <h1>Your Trusted <span class="text-accent">Moving Experts</span> in Halifax</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">Professional, friendly movers with clean trucks, tools, blankets &amp; dollies. Residential and commercial moves — local or long distance across Nova Scotia.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
          <a href="tel:+19029433003" class="btn btn-outline">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.362 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.338 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            (902) 943-3003
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-trust">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            Fully Insured
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            Free Equipment Included
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            Affordable Hourly Rates
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="assets/photos/photo_003.jpg" alt="MH Movers truck loaded and ready for a move in Halifax" class="hero-photo" fetchpriority="high">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="services" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-tag">What We Offer</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Moving &amp; Home Services</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">From local apartment moves to custom deck builds, our experienced team delivers quality results across Halifax and all of Nova Scotia.</p>
      <img src="assets/photos/editwebsite-mh-movers-can-1773937228713.jpg" alt="MH Movers professional moving team and truck ready for service" class="services-image">
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Residential Moving</h3>
          <p>Apartments, condos, and houses — we handle your belongings with care. 2 or 3 movers &amp; truck packages available at affordable hourly rates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Commercial Moving</h3>
          <p>Office relocations, retail moves, and warehouse transfers. We minimize your downtime with efficient planning and experienced crews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Long-Distance Moving</h3>
          <p>Moving across Nova Scotia or beyond? We plan every detail of your long-distance relocation so you can focus on settling in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13" rx="2"/><polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Truck &amp; Labor</h3>
          <p>Need a truck and crew? Hire our experienced movers by the hour. Clean trucks with blankets, dollies, and all the tools included free.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 3h18v18H3z"/><path d="M3 9h18"/><path d="M9 3v18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Decks &amp; Fencing</h3>
          <p>Custom-built decks, stairs, railings, and privacy fencing. Quality materials and craftsmanship that adds value to your home.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7"/><path d="M21 9v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Roofing</h3>
          <p>Roof replacements and repairs. Free inspections, financing available. Protect your home with professional roofing services.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About / Why Us -->
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="container about-inner">
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-tag">Why Choose Us</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Trusted Professionals, <br>Every Time</h2>
        <p>MH Movers and Truck was built on a simple promise: take the stress out of your move. Our professional, friendly team handles everything with care — from the first box to the last piece of furniture. We also bring the same dedication to our construction projects, building quality decks, fences, and roofs across 